  "Description": {
    "English": "The central processing unit of a Sentinel interceptor ship. The circuitry writhes microscopically, constantly rearranging itself as it scans for anomalies.<br><br>A vital component for any entity wishing to construct their own <span class=\"name name-technology\">Pilot Interface</span> for a Sentinel Interceptor.<br><br>Status: <span class=\"name name-fuel\">VOLATILE</span>",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一艘护卫拦截机的中央处理单元。在显微镜角度下，上面的电路永远在扭动重组，不停扫描着潜在的异象。<br><br>对任何想为护卫拦截机构建属于自己的<span class=\"name name-technology\">驾驶员接口</span>的实体而言，这都是至关重要的构件。<br><br>状态：<span class=\"name name-fuel\">不稳定</span>",
    "TraditionalChinese": "巡警攔截艦的中央處理單位。電路微微蠕動，不斷地重新排序，就像是在掃描異常一樣。<br><br>對任何想打造巡警攔截艦<span class=\"name name-technology\">駕駛員介面</span>的人來說，都是不可缺少的元件。<br><br>狀態：<span class=\"name name-fuel\">不穩定</span>。"
  },
