  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Harvest <span class=\"name name-special\">Hyaline Brains</span> from the remains of <span class=\"name name-special\">Sentinel Interceptor Ships</span>, lethal starcraft deployed to maintain law and order in regulated space.<br>Increase your <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Wanted Level</span> in space to engage <span class=\"name name-special\">System Authorities</span>",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "从<span class=\"name name-special\">护卫拦截机</span>的残骸收获<span class=\"name name-special\">透明质脑部</span>，这是一种专门被部署来维护受管制空间内的法治的致命飞船。<br>在太空中提高你的<span class=\"name name-fuel\">通缉等级</span>以吸引<span class=\"name name-special\">星系当局</span>的注意",
    "TraditionalChinese": "從當局部署在受管制太空內，維持法律與秩序的致命太空船：<span class=\"name name-special\">巡警攔截艦</span>殘骸採收<span class=\"name name-special\">透明大腦</span>。<br>提高你在太空中的<span class=\"name name-fuel\">通緝等級</span>，即可與<span class=\"name name-special\">星系當局</span>交戰"
